quran[9{c,v,t}:
21,73,"aur hum ne unn ko imam bana diya jo hamaray hukum se rahnumai karte thay aur hum ne inhen wahi ke zareya naik kamon ki aur namaz qaim karne aur zkoh dainay ki hadaayat ki, aur woh hamaray ibadat guzaar thay"
21,74,"aur loot ko hum ne hukum aur ilm bakhsha aur ussay uss bastii se bacha kar nikaal diya jobad karyan karti thi dar haqeeqat woh barri hi burii, fasik qoum thi"
21,75,"aur loot ko hum ne apni rehmat mein daakhil kya, woh Saleh logon mein se tha"
21,76,aur yahi Nemat hum ne Nooh ko di yaad karo jabkay inn sab se pehlay uss ne hamein puraka tha hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur usay aur is ke ghar walon ko karb azeem se nijaat di
21,77,"aur uss qoum ke muqablay mein uss ki madad ki jis ne hamari ayaat ko jhutla diya tha woh barray buray log thay, pas hum ne un sab ko ghark kar diya"
21,78,"aur isi Nemat se hum ne Dawood اaur Sulayman ko Sarfraz kya yaad karo woh mauqa jabkay woh dono aik khait ke muqadmay mein faisla kar rahay thay jis mein raat ke waqt doosray logon ki bakriyan phail gayi theen, aur hum unn ki adalat khud dekh rahay thay"
21,79,"uss waqt hum ne sahih faisla sulaiman ko samgha diya, halaank hukum aur ilm hum ne dono hi ko ataa kya tha Dawood ke sath hum ne pahoron aur parindon ko maskhar kar diya tha jo tasbeeh karte thay, iss feal ke karne walay hum hi thay"
21,80,"aur hum ne uss ko tumahray faiday ke liye zarah bananay ki sanat sikha di thi, taakay tum ko aik doosray ki maar se bachaaye, phir kya tum shukar guzaar ho ?"
21,81,"aur sulaiman ke liye hum ne taiz howa ko maskhar kar diya tha jo is ke hukum se uss sarzamen ki taraf chalti thi jis mein hum ne barkaten rakhi hain, hum har cheez ka ilm rakhnay walay thay"
